<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/A-beginner-s-guide-to-using-remote-sensing-for-offshore-tuna-fishing" title="A beginner’s guide to using remote sensing for offshore tuna fishing" alt="link">A beginner’s guide to using remote sensing for offshore tuna fishing</a></h2>

	
					<p>This <a href="http://www.spc.int/images/publications/en/Divisions/Fisheries/en-guide-using-remote-sensing.pdf" target="_blank">guide</a> was designed to give a very basic knowledge of remote sensing to offshore tuna fishermen.</p>
